Class UserLeafNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.coniks.coniks_server.TreeNode

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class UserLeafNode
extends LeafNode
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a leaf node containing a user's entry in the CONIKS key directory in the CONIKS binary Merkle prefix tree.
    See Also:

        public UserLeafNode clone(TreeNode parent)
        Clones (i.e. duplicates) this user leaf node with the given parent tree node.

        This function is called as part of the CONIKS Merkle tree rebuilding process at the beginning of every epoch.
